      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits significant wear and some fading. While it runs and drives fine, it would benefit from a tune-up and some cosmetic attention to bring it back to its best.",
