      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare standard of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been maintained to an exacting degree. This is an investment-grade example, offering peerless mechanical performance and an aesthetic presence indistinguishable from new. A definitive choice for the sophisticated collector.",
